values: I've recently decided that I no longer want to be in Lakeland. If anyone would like to donate to the "Help Zack move to London" fund. It would greatly be appreciated. I also need information of getting a new SS card mine was stolen and I need it to get a pass port. I'll gladly accept cash, money orders, and paypal. Or if anyone would like to come with me just let me know.

August, Loves to joke. Attractive. Suave and caring. Brave
and fearless.Firm and has leadership qualities.
Knows how to console others. Too generous and
egoistic. Takes high pride of oneself. Thirsty
for praises. Extraordinary spirit. Easily
angered. Angry when provoked. Easily jealous.
Observant. Careful and cautious. Thinks
quickly. Independent thoughts. Loves to lead
and to be led. Loves to dream. Talented in the
arts, music and defense. Sensitive but not
petty. Poor resistance against illnesses.
Learns to relax. Hasty and trusty. Romantic.
Loving and caring. Loves to make friends

Reality television loves it when people flip out and cry, last night I destroyed anything the Real World could ever film. My life seems like it is set for destroying me, or atleast my heart.
Nothing hurts more than being left in limbo by the one you're in love with.

So the mother fuckers at regal can suck a dick and die. The guy calls me at work and says "HEYYY GREAT NEWS BUDDY. This is Alex from Regal give me a call when you can" So I call Captain Dick face and he says "Hey Ive got some great news....we cant put you in the Mustang BUT I can get you in a 2000 civic" WHere is the great news? So Regal Auto can piss off because I now own a 2001 Mustang that Bennet Auto was kind enough to finance me for. So fuck you Regal.

One o'clock today I find out if the new owner of a black 2000 Mustang. I test drove it yesterday and it gave me an erection. It's so nice. Power everything, 20 inch black deep dish rims, and what really makes me happy....air conditioning. Lets hope I get it. I've never had a nice car before. The car I have doesnt even run anymore. Come onnnnnn Mustang.

Would the nonsense just please stop. For all of you that hate me just please quit. Everything is just getting ridiculous. You know who you are and you know I've tried to apologize and you won't listen. So, please stop the hate.
"Just stay with me, lay with me..." it makes me cry
It's starting to look like Im the guy people love to hate.
I think I'm set up to lose. In this whole situation nobody is on my side. She says she is in love, but she says she doesnt know what to do.

She makes me feel so...so untouchable, wonderful, perfect, happy, content, delightful, estatic, care free, wanted, loved, needed. Nights like last night are just amazing to me. I never feel better than when you're in my arms. I'm lucky to have someone as magnificent as you. I'm the most fortunate person to ever live. I'm in love with being in love.

7 a.m. comes way way too quickly. It seems like as soon as I close my eyes my alarm goes off. I do not like this morning thing. Work four to midnight sucked too, but now I get off at four so I don't know what to do with myself when I get off work. I just sit around my house and get fat.

I'm not a morning person at all. I havn't had to get up at seven since highschool. Working morning shift does give me lots of time in the afternoon to get stuff done. It's better than sleeping all day, going work, then going back to sleep.

The thought of losing you makes my stomach turn. I know in my heart that I have nothing to worry about, but I'm insecure right now. I know you love me, I know you're IN love with me. I just worry that's all. After losing you once I couldn't take a second time. It crushes my heart that your parents hate me. I figure in time they may grow to like me, but for now it kills me. 

I <3 Scooter
